{"tid":1585822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一單係爆樽打人 一單係疑似撕牆","createTime":"2019-09-21T17:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T18:31:29.000Z","uid":66379,"like":16,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f252cf95bc3e02c9a51a361887b03dbcba17305e","tid":1585822,"uid":66379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:27:51.000Z","msg":"有好多巴打混淆左兩單<br />\n<br />\n一單係疑似有白衣人追 後來被仆低<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1657299221267507/posts/2287649108232512/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1657299221267507%2Fposts%2F2287649108232512%2F&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=27a62099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1657299221267507/posts/2287649108232512/</a><br />\n<br />\n一單有點怪 都係最應該深思下 何為私了<br />\n就是我理解 睇直播係<br />\n有位呀叔被人覺得係撕過牆 只係表面有人講<br />\n但係疑似無動手打人 仲被跪低....<br />\n<br />\n要理解番兩單係分開 第一單無問題<br />\n第二單對方未企圖暴力之下就咁<br />\n係咪應該反思下 係咪有點over左私了動機低線 同時都令運動內部部激烈增多<br />\n反思對一場運動最重要<br />\n連對家都識用唔同方法 剛柔有別<br />\n宜家係咪應該要反思<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"771ca234965b538e38bd12dccc850b073f0fb59d","tid":1585822,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:29:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ab670abcaf25ff43d6c63fb8ba8110a0a175e1f7","tid":1585822,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:29:37.000Z","msg":"真係無辜? 今晚手足既行動靠你地廣傳啦<br />\n<br />\n今日兩位黑社會打市民在先「有片」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585676</a>"},{"pid":"017a92587e48be88a24ccbc18541053d04998f17","tid":1585822,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"43faf8b945355fdd75168c4db8868ac2c6437fab","tid":1585822,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:30:06.000Z","msg":"撕紙藍屍嗰單要搵證據<br />\n否則又畀人煲大 <br />\n<br />\n根本畀佢上的士就算啦 <br />\n<b